    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/e4e12385fcc3cd9f13d97c3ddad7461f.apng?t=1741302317\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/e4e12385fcc3cd9f13d97c3ddad7461f.poster.avif?t=1741302317\" class=\"bb_img\" width=566 height=99 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >红魔馆，已经变成了无尽的地牢！</h2>红魔馆是每进入一次就会改变其外观的地牢，这都是十六夜咲夜的功劳哦<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/44d92a6ed42361d0cee21f3d4e981cd2.poster.avif?t=1741302317\" width=574 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/44d92a6ed42361d0cee21f3d4e981cd2.webm?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/44d92a6ed42361d0cee21f3d4e981cd2.mp4?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>超过20个不同的可用角色！</strong></h2>用你最喜欢的角色来进行游戏吧！<br><br>目前抢先体验版中的可玩角色：<br>博丽灵梦、雾雨魔理沙、琪露诺、魂魄妖梦、露米娅、藤原妹红、红美铃、帕秋莉·诺蕾姬、十六夜咲夜、蕾米莉亚·斯卡蕾特、芙兰朵露·斯卡蕾特<br><u><strong>更多角色将在未来的更新中添加</strong></u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/6fa83bb91f2d33903e00a79cdae06a2a.poster.avif?t=1741302317\" width=574 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/6fa83bb91f2d33903e00a79cdae06a2a.webm?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/6fa83bb91f2d33903e00a79cdae06a2a.mp4?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>通过收集物品来加强你的角色！</strong></h2>利用快节奏的强化系统和丰富的道具，形成你的理想风格！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/31b595c2757059f91562eb6beb8a2f27.poster.avif?t=1741302317\" width=574 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/31b595c2757059f91562eb6beb8a2f27.webm?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/31b595c2757059f91562eb6beb8a2f27.mp4?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/133369bee87482df4f1218a90ac656d9.apng?t=1741302317\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/133369bee87482df4f1218a90ac656d9.poster.avif?t=1741302317\" class=\"bb_img\" width=566 height=128 /></picture></span>",
